Howto convert .odt file to text
depends on odt2txt --version
odt2txt 0.5
Copyright (c) 2006,2007 Dennis Stosberg <dennis@stosberg.net>

This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or
modify it under the terms of the GNU General Public License,
version 2 as published by the Free Software Foundation

https://github.com/dstosberg/odt2txt

odt2txt --output=out.txt wheeler-trusting-trust-ddc.33e940100d7a44a1b09be934bc17cb0e.odt
some information is lost by lack of font and flow of document and footnotes interrupted by conversion. Better to keep the PDF. 

Howto export odt to PDF on android 
depends on collabora app found here https://www.collaboraoffice.com/downloads/Collabora-Office-Android-Snapshot/
export is not PDF/A1a

